Class BinarySearchTree<T extends java.lang.Comparable<? super T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • BinarySearchTree<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of data element contained in the node.

    public class BinarySearchTree<T extends java.lang.Comparable<? super T>>
extends java.lang.Object
    Implements an unbalanced binary search tree. Note that all "matching" is based on the compareTo() method.
    Version:
    11.30.2017
    Author:
    Mark Allen Weiss (with modifications by John Lewis), Steven Shi
